<!-- wp:group {"metadata":{"name":"Lore Column 1a"},"className":"founders-lore-col","layout":{"type":"default"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group founders-lore-col">
<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"founders-lore-text","style":{"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-bone)"},"typography":{"fontFamily":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dfont-family\u002d\u002dlato)"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-color founders-lore-text" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-bone);font-family:var(--wp--preset--font-family--lato)">In the age before history was written, when the world still trembled with raw creation, four extraordinary souls discovered something that would change the course of existence forever. Deep within the Whispering Caverns, where reality grew thin and the boundaries between worlds dissolved like morning frost, they found the Amethyst Veil — a gem of impossible beauty that pulsed with the heartbeat of forgotten gods.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
